<header>
	<div class="header-mask"></div>
	<div class="header-slogan">
		<h2>為你的大學生活上色</h2>
		<p>搶先體驗專屬學生的各種便利服務</p>
	</div>
	<div class="header-call-to-action">
		<button class="btn btn--large">立即註冊 / 登入</button>
	</div>
	<div class="row row-inner-s" style="margin-top: 48px;">
		<div class="col m4 s12">
			<div class="service">
				<h4>TABLE</h4>
				<p>你的專屬行動課程表</p>
				<small>把你的課表帶著走，貼心提醒不再忘記上課時間、地點，上課變得好輕鬆</small>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col m4 s12">
			<div class="service">
				<h4>BOOKS</h4>
				<p>你的買書好幫手</p>
				<small>一本即團購價，線上金流系統，讓你買書更便宜、方便。</small>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col m4 s12">
			<div class="service">
				<h4>TASKS</h4>
				<p>尋找校園的即時幫手</p>
				<small>尋找需要幫忙的同學，賺取即時的外快，哪裡都幫、隨時都幫</small>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="slideshow-3d" style="display:none;">
		<div class="slideshow-3d-inner">
			<div class="layer layer1">
				<%= image_tag('table-img.png') %>
			</div>
			<div class="layer layer2">
				<%= image_tag('books-img.png') %>
			</div>
			<div class="layer layer3">
				<%= image_tag('paper-img.png') %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</header>
